      <h1 class="entry-title"><a href="/blog/2013/07/01/octopress-custom/">Octopress-custom</a></h1>
    
    
      <p class="meta">
        
  


  
    <span class="byline author vcard">by <span class="fn">Jiessie</span></span>
  

 - 
        








  


<time datetime="2013-07-01T03:45:00+08:00" pubdate data-updated="true">Jul 1<span>st</span>, 2013</time> - 
        


        
      </p>
    
  </header>


  <div class="entry-content"><h1>设置网站的description 和keywords</h1>

<p>在网页的head部分设置name 为description 和keywords 的meta元素可以让网页更容易被搜索引擎搜索到,在Octopress中设置首页(source/index.html)和每篇blog的description和keywords即可。</div>
  
  
